# Ablatus Command Center

This is a piece of Software, based on node.js and mongoDB.
It allows full Control over a net of ablati.

The Database holds the ablati, the gui allows to enter them manually.
Also you may enter an intercoma and use this to get ablati on this one.

The Gui allows to
- Get the Status
- Reconfigure
- Show the Topographs
- Stop, Start, Restart Ablati
- Try to get an Ablatus by using "identify" on an ip and port